abstract: All relevant ethical guidelines have been followed; any necessary IRB and/or ethics committee approvals have been obtained and details of the IRB/oversight body are included in the manuscript.
author: Fei Lin; Qingbian Ma; Qingtao Zhou; Zhonghua Deng; Lu Li; Hong Zhu; Xiaomei Tong; Xiaoguang Li; Jingjin Liang; Jie Xu; Ying Liang; Yongchang Sun; Xiaohua Wang; Biying Zhang
title: Prevalence and clinical features of 2019 novel coronavirus disease (COVID-19) in the Fever Clinic of a teaching hospital in Beijing: a single-center, retrospective study
